{"tid":299623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總訪港】警：金鐘灣仔北非常擠塞　　 冇必要就唔好去","createTime":"2017-06-27T08:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T14:23:29.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcb6564fd488853a3784e24fc548356ccba267c","tid":299623,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498552502_eec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498552502_eec9.jpg&h=1da33fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平與夫人彭麗媛本周四至周六將訪港3日，出席香港主權移交中國20周年活動及為新班子監誓。警務處助理處長（行動）鄭耀武表示，國家領導人在港活動和停留的區域，一帶都會設立「核心保安區」，分階段封閉。<br />\n<br />\n而國家領導人的車隊經過時，一帶都有人潮管制，強調金鐘、灣仔北一帶，屆時將「非常擠塞」，如無必要則盡量不要前往這些地區，並保持忍讓。"},{"pid":"99648fab5f324bde6fa1815fe1419e3ea5d6692b","tid":299623,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"阻人收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56c3ce42b53df677ed051bd9ee87059b4b2cd24","tid":299623,"uid":23707,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"習總唔好去咪得<br />\n<br />\nON9警"},{"pid":"743d8aef9caa79ed1b4ccc7836c1437b351d0715","tid":299623,"uid":102096,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e11f9ad6b11ca68ecb5d619ea6381452fbec65c","tid":299623,"uid":26672,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌好心就宣佈全港放假三天啦<br />\n香港市民對主席到訪都感到十分高興</blockquote><br />\n係，你真係要搞大龍鳳不如放下d濕鳩假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5f43eb687abe8e1ffec295fb71f573db2d2ec4","tid":299623,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"唔撚忍讓呀撚樣"},{"pid":"8f2d502778cfdfb3b086bbc35b8b3f0ab2e44715","tid":299623,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"港奴：唔使返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c82868b8ad4d223aa9c275a62f7e6a5d3cbdd08","tid":299623,"uid":11001,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾多罐午餐肉</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a7697347729b78f25c358f1d1b934c174802945","tid":299623,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌好心就宣佈全港放假三天啦<br />\n香港市民對主席到訪都感到十分高興</blockquote><br />\n由今日開始OT三日，港奴都會十分高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又解決到交通問題，一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95791fb65f48b00e407ab3827bcf15945b67ebfc","tid":299623,"uid":3473,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:08:24.000Z","msg":"攪到香港亂曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗返工呀？阻撚住曬，正一死廢青，讀屎片"},{"pid":"55e147ea8dcbb1e377b1363d7decd27f2abf3b0f","tid":299623,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾多罐午餐肉</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平周四（29日）訪港，警方昨日作相關保安行動的前期準備，包括在灣仔北一帶擺設水馬陣。消息指出，今次警方設定的「保安區」範圍將是歷來最大，設置的水馬數量亦將是歷來最多。警方亦要求附近一帶地盤今日起停工，以便派駐人員搜查及駐守。<br />\n<br />\n去年5月全國人大委員長張德江訪港時，警方將會展、君悅酒店、萬麗海景酒店及中環廣場一帶列為「保安區」，設置近200個水馬，當時已被指是「歷來最多」。消息指警方以反恐需要為由，今次將再度擴大「保安區」範圍，動用水馬「遠超此數」。本報昨觀察所見，港灣道、菲林明道及中環廣場一帶已陸續出現水馬陣，據稱警方將在周三晚前試驗不同水馬陣式，敲定陣式後才「入水」。<br />\n<br />\n坑渠貼封條 水馬遠超200個<br />\n<br />\n警方的重點搜查隊昨日到會展外圍巡查，逐一檢查坑渠口，並貼上黑色封條，以示「已檢查」。有在會展對出及金鐘地盤的工人昨對本報表示，已被通知今日起放假，下周一才復工，<span style=\"color: red;\">「無故沒了4天日薪」</span>。有警方消息透露，警方今明兩天派遣密閉空間搜查隊人員，搜索地盤每一角落及地底範圍，「以防有危險物品收藏」，並會在相關位置「做記號」以示已檢查，且會派員在習近平訪港期間駐守，「如發現記號有變，要重新檢查」。"},{"pid":"efe9ccf3294169249a3f717b325825161a9aa03c","tid":299623,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"佢數漏西九地盤，西九個臨時公園今日有黑警進駐"},{"pid":"b43efddd15262546de13dea5cdd76bb98114a602","tid":299623,"uid":42820,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"肯額外放兩日公眾假期<br />\n民怨少好多"},{"pid":"eb2de2950e889d29e2315aea42f933db2b13128f","tid":299623,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"唔好逼哂去旺角，please"},{"pid":"9cd16585bc78406024ace0c64bfb75ea232145e3","tid":299623,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯額外放兩日公眾假期<br />\n民怨少好多</blockquote><br />\n去撚哂台灣日本啦, 仲邊有民怨"},{"pid":"f354930d79b0ad95986df21860f5f4c9232c0c0a","tid":299623,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯額外放兩日公眾假期<br />\n民怨少好多</blockquote><br />\n工聯會會肯咩"},{"pid":"0bcf7456cc92f7c783093fee910872348b68e6ed","tid":299623,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:13:16.000Z","msg":"放工時間地鐵又跪低就好笑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad056ea674b244e2325849ac554ce26cef3c037","tid":299623,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>肯額外放兩日公眾假期<br />\n民怨少好多</blockquote><br />\n工聯會會肯咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出黎數午餐肉未？"},{"pid":"2bd89cefb82eb924ea01abb0c921b95764972313","tid":299623,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老妹 點去搵錢愛國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f012f53af8caa61bde2e16eb2fba4c09914db44b","tid":299623,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,